Name: Aura Biosciences Inc
Description: Aura Biosciences Inc is a clinical-stage biotechnology company dedicated to revolutionizing cancer treatment through its proprietary virus-like particle (VLP) technology. The company’s lead therapeutic candidate, AU-011, specifically targets ocular cancers by selectively destroying tumor cells while preserving adjacent healthy tissues. Aura is advancing its clinical pipeline to address critical unmet needs in oncology, supported by a strong management team and strategic partnerships. With a focus on innovation and a commitment to rigorous clinical trials, Aura Biosciences is well-positioned as a leader in the development of targeted cancer therapies in a rapidly evolving market.
Address: 80 GUEST STREET, BOSTON, MA, UNITED STATES, 02135
